Usage
The full model is wrapped inside a single Python script called Scale_Aging_Inference_Script_Image_Only.py. To execute, run the following command in a command line terminal:
python Scale_Aging_Inference_Script_Image_Only.py &lt;img_dir&gt; &lt;csv_dir&gt; &lt;model_dir&gt;
where







&lt;img_dir&gt;
(str) full path to the directory containing the scale images to process


&lt;csv_dir&gt;
(str) full path to desired directory to which the CSV output will be written


&lt;model_dir&gt;
(str) full path to the directory containing the trained model weights (i.e., the best_model.pth file)

